ActMi'kmaq Education Act
SubjectOrder Adding the Glooscap First Nation to the Schedule to the Mi'kmaq Education Act
PrecisOrder Adding the GLOOSCAP FIRST NATION TO THE SCHEDULE TO THE MI'KMAQ EDUCATION ACT in order to enable the First Nation to benefit from the same control over education and complementary programming as the other signatories to the Agreement.
